Package: modalcc
Title: Modified Arcsine-Log Calibration Curve
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Adrian", "Correndo", , "correndo@ksu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4172-289X"))
Description: the modalcc package assists on the estimation of critical soil test values for a target relative yield with confidence intervals following the modified ALCC model originally described by Dyson and Conyers (2013) and modified by Correndo et al. (2017).
